      "component_type": "ApiNode",
      "id": "generate",
      "name": "Generate image prompts via /api/llm-bridge",
      "url": "{{CINATRA_BASE_URL}}/api/llm-bridge",
      "http_method": "POST",
      "data": {
        "agent_id": "blog-image-prompt-agent",
        "system": "You are a stateless blog image-prompt generator. Follow the SKILL.md step-by-step. Return a single JSON object with {prompts, notes} \u2014 nothing else.",
        "user": "Generate {{ count }} blog-image prompts for the supplied draft.\n\nDraft (JSON): {{ draft }}\n\nDistribute the prompts across these placements (default: cover, inline, social): {{ placements }}\n\nVisual style guidance (may be empty): {{ style }}\n\nBrand keywords to weave in (may be empty array): {{ brandKeywords }}\n\nReturn ONLY the JSON object specified in SKILL.md \u2014 keys: prompts (array of {placement, prompt, rationale}), notes (string).\n- contextSlotBindings: {{ contextSlotBindings }}",
        "agent_run_id": "{{ agent_run_id }}",
        "cinatra_llm": {
          "preferredProvider": "openai",
          "preferredModel": "gpt-5.5"
        }
      },
      "inputs": [
        {
          "title": "draft",
          "type": "object"
        },
        {
          "title": "count",
          "type": "integer"
        },
        {
          "title": "placements",
          "type": "array",
          "json_schema": {
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "style",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "title": "brandKeywords",
          "type": "array",
          "json_schema": {
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "agent_run_id",
          "type": "string"
        },
        {
          "title": "contextSlotBindings",
          "type": "array",
          "json_schema": {
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "artifactId": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "representationRevisionId": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "semanticAssertionId": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "extension": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "sourceScope": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "ownerId": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "title": "prompts",
          "type": "array",
          "json_schema": {
            "items": {
              "type": "object"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "notes",
          "type": "string"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "cinatra": {
          "riskClass": "read_only",
          "requiresApproval": false,
          "packageName": "@cinatra-ai/blog-image-prompt-agent",
          "description": "Single ApiNode \u2192 /api/llm-bridge. Bridge auto-discovers SKILL.md from agents/cinatra/blog-image-prompt-agent/skills/blog-image-prompt-agent/SKILL.md (via agent_id). No toolboxes \u2014 the LLM generates image prompts from the supplied draft using its own world knowledge; no MCP primitive calls, no web_search needed."
        }
      }
    },
